headline: Macau Gaming Revenue Falls Short; Las Vegas Sands, Wynn Resorts, MGM In Focus
summary: Macau gaming revenue rose 14.8% in December vs. a year earlier, less than expected. That could affect shares of Las Vegas Sands, Wynn Resorts and MGM.
